    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Жисмоний шахслар ўртасида тузилган кўчмас мол-мулк олди-сотди шартномасининг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#2}Тасдиқлов ёзуви тасдиқланган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ушбу шартномани мен – Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Нотариал идора жойлашган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да жойлашган хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> тарафларнинг хоҳиш-иродасига ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси қонун ҳужжатларига асосан тасдиқладим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Шартнома тарафлар томонидан менинг ҳузуримда ўқиб, имзолади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Тарафларнинг шахси аниқланди, уларнинг муомалага лаёқатлилиги ва сотилаётган уй-жой сотувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Уй-жойни сотган шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">га тегишлилиги текширилди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Шахсий мулоқот давомида тарафларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизлигига шубҳа туғилмади ва ушбу нотариал ҳаракатни амалга ошириш даврида нотариал идорада уларнинг муомалага лаёқатсизликлари ҳақида ҳеч қандай маълумотлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 481-моддасига асосан ушбу шартнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Туман (шаҳар) кадаст агентлиги</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> Иқтисодиёт ва молия вазирлиги ҳузуридаги Кадастр агентлигида давлат рўйхатидан ўтказилиши лозим.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Реестрга </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Шартноманинг реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Давлат божи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Ундириладиган давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#5}Ҳуқуқий ва техник тусдаги қўшимча ҳаракатлар учун ундириладиган тўловлар миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> (имзо)</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>М.Ў.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
